Code preview of 资金明细表sl_fund_detail

drop table if exists sl_fund_detail;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_fund_detail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_fund_detail
(
fundDetailId bigint(20) not null auto_increment comment 'id号',
fundIntentId bigint(20) comment '款项表id',
fundQlideId bigint(20) comment '资金流水表id',
afterMoney numeric(10,2) comment '对帐金额',
overdueNum smallint(6) comment '逾期天数',
overdueAccrual numeric(10,2) comment '逾期利息',
operTime datetime comment '操作时间',
primary key (fundDetailId)
);

alter table sl_fund_detail comment '资金明细表';

alter table sl_fund_detail add constraint FK_FK_FUNDDETAIL_FINDITEM_REC foreign key (fundIntentId)
references sl_fund_intent (fundIntentId) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table sl_fund_detail add constraint FK_FK_FUNDDETAIL_QLIDE_FEC foreign key (fundQlideId)
references sl_fund_qlide (fundQlideId) on delete restrict on update restrict;
